			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion

			}
		}

		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Argollea = {
	color = { 109 53 12 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Locrlepreder

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Olbimyosia = {
	color = { 195 62 17 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Nirmylalous

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Gourdorylea = {
	color = { 180 191 20 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Orelefkaai

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	k_France = {
		color = { 0 128 255 }

	color = { 227 168 27 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Calliankica

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Megalomonasica = {
	color = { 136 128 35 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Bythcherspolis

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	k_Goaegatrea = {
		color = { 136 128 35 }

		capital = c_Bythcherspolis

		can_create = {
			NOT = {
				faith = {
					religion_tag = christianity_religion
					has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
				}
			}
		}

		ai_primary_priority = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
				}
				add = @correct_culture_primary_score
			}
		}

		d_Megalomonasica = {

e_Massaimbrlia = {
	color = { 36 95 75 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Metapantipdia

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Laoononia = {
	color = { 184 155 84 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Galilaera

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}
